title: Day 1 adult uninjured, bio rep 1
treatment_protocol_ch1: Paralytic Injury on Precellys 24 (max settings, 20 sec) in M9 or only incubation in M9 (uninjured).
growth_protocol_ch1: Egg synchronization by hypochlorite treatment followed by growth at 25C.
extract_protocol_ch1: Qiazol extraction followed by purification with RNeasy mini kit.
label_protocol_ch1: cRNA was biotinylated according to the standard Affymetrix protocol.
description.2: Day 1 adult C. elegans without injury
data_processing: Data were processed with Bioconductor according to the GC-RMA method, including quantile normalization, chip averaging, and background adjustment.
